    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @tedlin182, I will ask you the same thing than for your previous question, can you add a little gif showing the behavior you currently get and what is wrong with it? Can you also add a snippet of code to understand the element you are using?\r\n\r\nTo clear the query you have several options:\r\n* if the `searchState` of `<InstantSearch/>` is externalized you can modify the `searchState` by resetting the key `query` to an empty string.\r\n* You can use the connectSearchBox connector to build a custom component which will have the responsability to clear the query (by calling the refine function with an empty string). ",
