    "body": "Hi @mthuret \r\n\r\nYeah I currently am just passing down a custom `clearSearchField` method from my parent search component down to the results components and triggering that `onClick` which just sets `query: ''`.\r\n\r\nI wasn't sure if there was a less manual way of doing this, but for now this seems to work.\r\n\r\nThanks",
